<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Free Consultation Request - ReCounting</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fafc;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f4c68 0%, #143649 100%);
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 180px;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #1e293b;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .message {
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .info-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f5f9 0%, #f4f8f6 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #1f4c68;
    }
    .info-box-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1f4c68;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .info-item {
      display: flex;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #334155;
      min-width: 140px;
    }
    .info-value {
      color: #64748b;
    }
    .expectation-list {
      margin: 25px 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .expectation-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #475569;
    }
    .expectation-icon {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c1fd73, #a0e95e);
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-right: 14px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      color: #1f4c68;
    }
    .expectation-icon svg {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f4c68 0%, #143649 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(31, 76, 104, 0.4);
    }
    .footer {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f4c68 0%, #143649 100%);
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-text {
      color: #e2e8f0;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer-link {
      color: #c1fd73;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .social-links {
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .social-links a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 8px;
      color: #c1fd73;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .social-links a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://recounting.my.id/assets/ReCounting_Logo_Accounting_Services.png" alt="ReCounting Logo" class="logo">
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="greeting">Hi {{name}},</h2>

      <p class="message">
        Thank you for requesting a free consultation with ReCounting! We're excited to learn more about your business and how we can help with your bookkeeping and tax compliance needs.
      </p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-box-title">Your Request Details</div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-label">Service Interest:</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{service}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-label">Transaction Volume:</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{transaction_volume}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-label">Email:</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{email}}</span>
        </div>
        {{#if phone}}
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-label">Phone:</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{phone}}</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
      </div>

      <p class="message">
        <strong>What happens next:</strong>
      </p>

      <ul class="expectation-list">
        <li class="expectation-item">
          <span class="expectation-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span>Our senior accountant will review your information within 2 hours during business days</span>
        </li>
        <li class="expectation-item">
          <span class="expectation-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span>We'll contact you via WhatsApp or email to schedule your 30-minute discovery call</span>
        </li>
        <li class="expectation-item">
          <span class="expectation-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span>You'll receive personalized recommendations for your bookkeeping and tax compliance needs</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{whatsappUrl}}" class="cta-button">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
      </div>

      <p class="message">
        If you have any questions or need immediate assistance, feel free to reach out to us directly:
      </p>

      <p class="message">
        <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{companyEmail}}" class="footer-link">{{companyEmail}}</a><br>
        <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> <a href="{{whatsappUrl}}" class="footer-link">{{companyPhone}}</a>
      </p>

      <p class="message">
        We look forward to helping your business grow!
      </p>

      <p class="message">
        Best regards,<br>
        <strong>The ReCounting Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p class="footer-text">
        You're receiving this email because you requested a free consultation at ReCounting.
      </p>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://recounting.my.id">Website</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/6281139404640">WhatsApp</a>
        <a href="mailto:{{companyEmail}}">Email</a>
      </div>
      <p class="footer-text" style="margin-top: 15px;">
        Â© {{year}} ReCounting. All rights reserved. Part of <a href="https://balimicrotechnology.com" style="color: #c1fd73; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;">Bali Micro Technology</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
